Year-in-review summary: volume, time patterns, top contacts, reply discipline, storage, newsletters, superlatives. Like Spotify Wrapped but for your inbox

Usage: mxr wrapped [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --ytd                      Year-to-date (default if no window flag given): Jan 1 → now
      --year <YEAR>              Specific calendar year (Jan 1 → Dec 31 UTC)
      --since-days <SINCE_DAYS>  Last N days. Useful for quarterly or ad-hoc reviews
      --account <ACCOUNT>        
      --format <FORMAT>          [possible values: table, json, jsonl, csv, ids]
  -h, --help                     Print help
